{"tid":1858322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦再現恐襲　數人被刺警向刀手開槍","createTime":"2020-02-02T15:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T16:12:14.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7cecb6f28211e35b588d1ccebc33110a06b889fe","tid":1858322,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200202/photo/bkn-20200202232824742-0202_00912_001_01b.jpg?20200202233956\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200202%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200202232824742-0202_00912_001_01b.jpg%3F20200202233956&h=4af35cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員趕到現場處理。<br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦再發生恐襲，南部斯特雷特姆（Streatham）周日（2日）有多人在街頭被刺傷，警員到場開槍制服刀手，暫未知其情況，警方指事件涉及恐怖主義。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的照片可見，一名男子倒臥在一間藥房外，持槍警員則擎槍指向該名男子，有指他被擊斃，但警方未有公布。也有未經證實的消息指，該名男子胸口綁有物件，未知是否爆炸裝置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200202/bkn-20200202232824742-0202_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200202%2Fbkn-20200202232824742-0202_00912_001.html&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=3835401d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200202/bkn-20200202232824742-0202_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5485e6ba0825f9c2a367c562b16ba1178f9258d7","tid":1858322,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:47:44.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢譯名嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc878955789cd3268f6fbc8088a0c31650bfef1","tid":1858322,"uid":85168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:06:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pscp.tv/w/1LyGBNeApOaGN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pscp.tv%2Fw%2F1LyGBNeApOaGN&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=58